summary: 检测万户 ezOFFICE 系统中 wf_process_attrelate_aiframe.jsp 文件是否存在 SQL 注入漏洞，该漏洞可能允许未授权攻击者获取数据库权限并进一步控制服务器。
summary_en: Detect SQL injection vulnerability in the wf_process_attrelate_aiframe.jsp file of Ten thousand House ezOFFICE system. This vulnerability may allow unauthenticated attackers to gain database privileges and further control the server.
